  '<p><strong>Total Probability:</strong> $P(A) = \sum P(A|B_i)P(B_i)$</p><p><strong>Bayes'' Theorem:</strong> Reverses conditional probability.<br>$P(B_i | A) = \frac{P(A | B_i) P(B_i)}{P(A)}$</p>',
